a%2C%20and%20both%20of%20them%20are%20employed%2C%20earning%20about%20%243%2C400%20a%20month%20total.%20Mixson%20is%20building%20savings%20to%20have%20top%20surgery%20in%20the%20next%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBritt%20and%20Mixson%20are%20part%20of%20a%20cohort%20of%20about%2091%20million%20Americans%20who%20cannot%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-struggle-afford-healthcare-medicaid-low-income-black-hispanic-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eafford%20or%20don't%20have%20access%20to%20quality%20medical%20care%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20study%20from%20the%20UCLA%20Williams%20Institute%20also%20found%20that%20while%20transgender%20people%20have%20high%20rates%20of%20enrollment%20in%20health%20insurance%2C%201%20in%203%20avoid%20seeking%20healthcare%20because%20of%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20lot%20to%20struggle%20with%2C%20and%20it's%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20Mixon%20said%2C%20of%20his%20journey%20to%20afford%20surgery%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20it's%20so%20rewarding%20at%20the%20same%20time%20to%20just%20wake%20up%20and%20not%20feel%20so%20shitty%20about%20yourself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20wedding%20picture%20shows%20the%20bride%20shoving%20cake%20up%20the%20groom's%20nose.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6839f57eca50259add4d6106%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20married%20couple%20moved%20to%20Ohio%20in%20search%20of%20an%20affirming%20community%20but%20had%20to%20leave%20because%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20living.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Mixson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22952acd25-aecb-4e53-b76b-62368dfc0c8a%5C%22%3EFinding%20community%20and%20fundraising%20for%20gender-affirming%20medical%20care%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMixson%20works%20as%20a%20front%20desk%20receptionist%2C%20and%20his%20wife%20is%20a%20remote%20IT%20worker.%20Since%20spiraling%20into%20debt%2C%20the%20two%20have%20had%20to%20cut%20amenities%20like%20eating%20out%20and%20have%20chosen%20to%20prioritize%20rebuilding%20their%20emergency%20savings%20over%20paying%20back%20their%20medical%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20spend%20over%20half%20of%20their%20combined%20monthly%20paychecks%20on%20rent%2C%20transportation%2C%20utilities%2C%20and%20food%2C%20leaving%20them%20with%20about%20%24100%20a%20month%20to%20set%20aside%20for%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20haven't%20paid%20a%20medical%20bill.%20I%20just%20kind%20of%20let%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Fdoes-medical-debt-affect-credit-score%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esit%20on%20my%20credit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Mixson%20said.%20Britt%20was%20finally%20diagnosed%20with%20POTS%20this%20past%20month%20and%20is%20receiving%20proper%20treatment%20for%20it%20while%20working%20remotely.%20The%20newfound%20stability%20has%20allowed%20the%20pair%20to%20schedule%20Mixson's%20top%20surgery%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMixson%20estimates%20that%20if%20insurance%20doesn't%20cover%20his%20top%20surgery%2C%20he'll%20be%20on%20the%20hook%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.folxhealth.com%2Flibrary%2Ftop-surgery-101-procedures-cost-and-safety%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanother%20%2410%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20has%20saved%20some%20of%20that%20amount%20and%20started%20a%20GoFundMe%20to%20raise%20an%20additional%20%243%2C500.%20Mixson%20said%20it's%20been%20hard%20to%20fundraise%20from%20the%20small%20queer%20community%20in%20his%20hometown%2C%20as%20he%20said%20most%20are%20also%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMixson%20has%20been%20posting%20to%20Reddit%20forums%20about%20his%20fundraiser%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20reach%20a%20wider%20audience%20online%20and%20garner%20more%20support.%20As%20of%20March%2031%2C%20he's%20only%20raised%20%24980%20toward%20his%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20his%20close%20friends%20have%20been%20pivotal%20in%20helping%20him%20figure%20out%20things%20like%20insurance%20and%20extending%20cash%20in%20times%20of%20need%2C%20including%20%24200%20when%20he%20moved%2C%20so%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20could%20buy%20groceries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20a%20selfie%2C%20a%20married%20queer%20couple%20smile%20while%20sitting%20on%20a%20couch.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6839f5c4c6ad288d14823f3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlex%20and%20his%20wife%20often%20have%20to%20navigate%20the%20difficulty%20of%20being%20a%20queer%20couple%20in%20a%20conservative%20city.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Mixson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Mixson%2C%20top%20surgery%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20safety%20in%20being%20able%20to%20pass%20as%20a%20cisgender%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20starting%20testosterone%2C%20he%20said%2C%20few%20people%20recognize%20him%20from%20before%20his%20transition%2C%20but%20in%20the%20small%20city%2C%20word%20spreads%20quickly.%20There%20are%20moments%20when%20Mixson%20is%20afraid%20he'll%20be%20recognized.%20He's%20even%20more%20worried%20since%20the%20election%2C%20given%20that%20the%20Trump%20administration%20has%20pulled%20funding%20from%20institutions%20that%20work%20on%20DEI-related%20projects%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2025%2F01%2Fdefending-women-from-gender-ideology-extremism-and-restoring-biological-truth-to-the-federal-government%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epurged%20inclusive%20language%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20mention%20of%20transgender%20people%20on%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnbc-out%2Fout-politics-and-policy%2Fgovernment-agencies-scrub-lgbtq-web-pages-remove-info-trans-intersex-p-rcna190519%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20federal%20websites%2C%3C%2Fa%3E