f%20Tech%3A%20Europe%2C%20and%20organizer%20of%20multiple%20AI%20hackathons%20across%20the%20continent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20changed%20with%20the%20AI%20boom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWiertz%20said%20that%2C%20since%20the%20arrival%20of%20ChatGPT%20in%20late%202022%2C%20more%20research%20labs%20and%20AI%20startups%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheres-how-agi-house-bays-hottest-artificial-intelligence-hacker-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Earranging%20hackathons%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20cities%20with%20less%20%26quot%3Btech%20organization%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20bring%20together%20top%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20events'%20talent-pulling%20power%20is%20making%20hackathons%20%26quot%3Ba%20viable%20way%20for%20hot%20AI%20startups%20to%20compete%20with%20Big%20Tech%20for%20a%20top%20talent%20pool%2C%26quot%3B%20Zoe%20Qin%2C%20vice%20president%20at%20Dawn%20Capital%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-hackathons-2017-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Tech%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20typically%20have%20a%20major%20advantage%20over%20startups%20in%20the%20talent%20market%3A%20they%20can%20outspend%20them%20in%20recruitment%20and%20entice%20candidates%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-workers-real-winners-ai-talent-war-pay-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esubstantial%20compensation%3C%2Fa%3E%20packages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHackathons%20are%20one%20way%20for%20startups%20to%20level%20the%20playing%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStartups%20cannot%20spend%20as%20much%20money%20on%20LinkedIn%20ads%20or%20copy%20what%20Big%20Tech%20do%20in%20terms%20of%20prestige%2C%20but%20they%20can%20show%20that%20they're%20more%20agile%2C%20and%20more%20approachable%2C%20that%20they're%20more%20committed%20during%20a%20hackathon%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Benjamin%20Wolba%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20European%20Defense%20Tech%20Hub%2C%20which%20organizes%20hackathons%20across%20the%20continent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20startups%20use%20hackathons%20to%20scout%20early-career%20talent%20that%20they%20might%20not%20reach%20during%20traditional%20hiring%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAngelo%20Giacco%2C%20an%20Imperial%20College%20London%20and%20ETH%20Zurich%20graduate%2C%20participated%20in%20an%20AI%20hackathon%20organized%20by%20ElevenLabs%20in%20November.%20Two%20weeks%20later%2C%20he%20landed%20a%20job%20offer%20as%20an%20engineer%20at%20the%20AI%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20even%20have%20considered%20applying%20if%20I%20hadn't%20gone%20to%20the%20hackathon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20now%20hiring%20a%20few%20more%20people%20from%20hackathons%2C%20and%20we've%20launched%20one%20in%20seven%20different%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20junior%20roles.%20Dawn%20Capital's%20Qin%20said%20that%20after%20some%20hackathons%2C%20she's%20seen%20some%20startups%20go%20after%20%26quot%3Bhigh-performing%20candidates%2C%20or%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20hackathon%20run%20by%20a%20tech%20company%20itself%2C%20their%20engineers%20who%20have%20performed%20really%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20AI%20startups%20want%20entrepreneurial%20talent%20that's%20not%20rooted%20in%20a%20specific%20background%2C%20and%20recruiting%20from%20a%20hackathon%20allows%20these%20upstarts%20to%20find%20people%20%26quot%3Bwho%20want%20to%20tinker%2C%20build%2C%20and%20make%20things%20better%20%E2%80%94%20who%20may%20not%20necessarily%20match%20a%20classic%20profile%20of%20a%20computer%20scientist%20who%20wants%20to%20work%20in%20Big%20Tech%2C%26quot%3B%20Qin%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hackathon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6835ad04c6ad288d1481ea9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%7BTech%3A%20Europe%7D%20AI%20Hackathon%20Berlin.%3Cp%3EBela%20Wiertz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20traditional%20AI%20research%20labs%20may%20not%20hire%20pure%20research%20talent%20from%20hackathons%2C%20it's%20useful%20for%20them%20to%20source%20solutions%20and%20customer-facing%20engineers%20who%20can%20build%20up%20the%20technology%20at%20the%20application%20layer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20foundation%20labs%20and%20all%20the%20infrastructure%20partners%20like%20Mistral%20and%20Eleven%20Labs%2C%20they're%20labs%2C%20but%20they're%20selling%20their%20technology%20as%20an%20infrastructure%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Wiertz.%20%26quot%3BSo%20for%20them%2C%20yes%2C%20it's%20about%20hiring%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20technology%20in%20the%20ecosystem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224aeeea18-04a2-4847-a87b-009f8b3c77c1%5C%22%3ENon-technical%20talent%20also%20has%20a%20shot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIncreasingly%2C%20more%20people%20from%20non-technical%20backgrounds%20are%20using%20AI%20coding%20assistants%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-vc-technical-founders-skills-investors-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evibe%20code%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20create%20technical%20products.%20That%20has%20lowered%20the%20barrier%20to%20entry%20for%20coding-related%20projects%20and%20broadened%20the%20talent%20pool%20that%20participates%20in%20hackathons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUniversity%20can%20be%20so%20theoretical%2C%20but%20hackathons%20help%20us%20to%20tackle%20real-life%20problems%20and%20get%20projects%20off%20the%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Franziska%20Harzheim%2C%20a%20venture%20scout%20at%20Flashpoint%20who%20has%20participated%20in%20multiple%20AI%20hackathons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20degree%20in%20business%20analytics%2C%20Harzheim%20has%20still%20found%20a%20way%20to%20leverage%20her%20background%20to%20build%20an%20AI%20product%20with%20a%20team.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20those%20hackathons%20are%20not%20about%20having%20a%20team%20of%20five%20super-experienced%20coders.%20It's%20more%20like%20we%20look%20at%20everyone's%20skill%20set%2C%20and%20according%20to%20that%2C%20we%20divide%20the%20tasks%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20willing%20to%20learn%20something%20new%20on%20the%20spot%2C%20this%20is%20your%20space%2C%20it's%20amazing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20also%20a%20valuable%20opportunity%20for%20companies%20to%20assess%20potential%20candidates%20from%20technical%20and%20non-technical%20backgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20get%20to%20see%20how%20people%20perform%2C%20whether%20they%20earn%20the%20food%20or%20are%20actually%20doing%20stuff%20in%20real%20life%2C%20not%20in%20an%20assessment%20center%2C%26quot%3B%20European%20Defense%20Tech%20Hub's%20Wolba%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20get%20to%20see%20them%20working%20on%20the%20inside%20%E2%80%94%20it%20could%20be%20very%20information%20dense%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20time-effective%20way%20to%20understand%20whether%20you%20want%20to%20work%20with%20this%20person.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-hackathons-ai-talent-big-tech-jobs-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748674802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6812020e3fe8d3928364742a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-hackathons-ai-talent-big-tech-jobs-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hackathons%20are%20becoming%20a%20key%20talent-scouting%20opportunity%20for%20AI%20startups%20to%20attract%20diverse%20talent%20at%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20their%20career.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rkanetkar%40insider.com%20(Riddhi%20Kanetkar)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A324%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-hackathons-ai-talent